name: Mellow Window Scene
description:
This print of a mellow window scene is part of the ‘at home’ series created with old school film and printed from negative.

	<sub>~~</sub><sub>~~
-a 8×10 print from an original photograph on matt photo paper with a white border.
-print may vary slightly due to photograph dimensions.
-each print is numbered and signed on the back and is carefully packaged with tissue lining in a heavy duty envelope.
-each print comes with a short description about the setting and why the moment was captured.
-goods are posted by airmail using australia post services.
~</sub><sub>~~</sub>~
